<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The core difference lies in the onboarding process. Regulated entities require government ID, facial scanning, and proof of address before you can trade a single dollar. On the other hand, the best no KYC crypto exchanges allow you to register with just an email address and start trading immediately. This speed is a significant advantage for traders who want to buy Bitcoin without verification to catch a moving market.</span></p>
