<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Active traders can’t afford to wait around, prices change in seconds. We tested download and upload speeds to ensure that even when using the<a href="https://ventureburn.com/best-crypto-exchange-for-day-trading/" data-wpel-link="internal"> <b>best crypto exchange for day trading</b></a>, your execution remains instant and slippage-free. We also checked latency from North American, European, and Asian servers to determine the fastest vpn for crypto trading. To eliminate peculiar spikes, we tested at various times during the day, and averaged the results. VPNs that performed relatively well, no matter the distance of the servers, were ranked the highest on our list.</span></p>
