</ul>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This is why many experienced traders follow a simple rule: don’t use a VPN during KYC. Complete verification on your normal network or connect to a VPN server in your home country if absolutely necessary. After KYC is approved, VPN usage usually becomes less of an issue especially when used for security rather than location spoofing. The key is timing and consistency.</span></p>
